subject: Soccer
UEFA Champions League (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Olivier Giroud, who seemed to be complaining nonstop Wednesday night, was ejected before halftime as Arsenal lost, 2-1, to Dinamo Zagreb in the Champions League.
